   <div class="post_main_title">
    17华工翻硕经验帖
   </div> 
   <div class="post_params clearfix"> 
    <a href="forum.php?mod=forumdisplay&amp;fid=2076&amp;page=4&amp;mobile=2" class="belong">来自：<span>2017考研复试现场直击</span> <strong>&gt;</strong></a> 
